com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.mrcm

Interface CardinalityPredicate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, ConceptModelComponent, ConceptModelPredicate, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CardinalityPredicateImpl

    public interface CardinalityPredicate
extends ConceptModelPredicate
    A representation of the model object 'Cardinality Predicate'. Predicate representing an MRCM cardinality check.

    The following features are supported:

    • Min Cardinality
    • Max Cardinality
    • Group Rule
    • Predicate

    See Also:
    MrcmPackage.getCardinalityPredicate()
